      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-amali-saduq:53:3",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/29/1/54/3",
      "text": [
        ": قال رسول الله (صلى الله عليه وآله): من فارق جماعة المسلمين فقد خلع ربقة الاسلام من عنقه، قيل: يا رسول الله، وما جماعة المسلمين؟ قال: جماعة أهل الحق وإن قلوا (2)."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bilal-muhammad": [
          "By this isnad, he said: The Messenger of Allah (s) said: Whoever splits away from the Muslim community has taken the collar of Islam off his neck. It was said: O Messenger of Allah! What is the Muslim community? He said: The community of the people of truth, even if they are few."
        ]
      }
    },
    "verse_translations": [
      "en.bilal-muhammad"
    ]
